{"word":"ἀπαρτάω","slug":"ἀπαρτάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀπαρτάω</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to hang up from</i>, <el>ἀπ. δέρην</el> <i>to strangle</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to hang loose</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>to make dependent upon</i>, <el>ἐξ ἑαυτοῦ</el> <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to detach, separate</i>, <el>τί τινος</el> <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>ἀπηρτημένοι</el> <i>detached, disunited</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> in <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>Act.</a></a> <i>to remove oneself, go away</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}